name:
  fiber-bundles
version:
  0.1.0
synopsis:
  Fiber bundles and related algebraic structures.
description:
  This package defines a @FiberBundle@ class and supporting classes that allow
  the manipulation of types as fiber bundles whose fibers have an algebraic
  structure.
